{"tid":1488980,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"咪撚再屌啦求下你地","createTime":"2019-08-19T18:05:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T18:50:40.000Z","uid":289818,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"96779552b416503ca79a412ae7412d24ab35412e","tid":1488980,"uid":289818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T18:05:56.000Z","msg":"朝早屌塞鐵,晏就屌follow狗乸,夜晚屌找數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當中有抵鬧係事實,但唔好忘記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">睇得連登既都係手足,對自己人絕對唔應該係屌!</span><br />\n<br />\n你可以提<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以開post講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但絕對唔可以用屌柒人既方式表演呢樣野!因為呢班係自己人!佢地唔係對家!更加唔可以出到割席呢種字眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n邊個想我地互屌,大家心知肚明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連登屌柒熱狗同時自己亦都比人帶風向做左熱狗既角色<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後,想為塞鐵講兩句,嗌左光復香港 時代革命咁耐,你地係咪又真係明天琦所講既兄弟爬山呢?<br />\n<br />\n不如大家睇下條片,睇下天琦點講?我唔支持再搞塞鐵,不過我唔會屌呢班想做野既手足<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以後邊個想屌人、互屌、對自己人有不滿，就望住呢堆相<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1471935\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1471935</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VEUhAVki0DA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVEUhAVki0DA&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NAEcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=3bdaab85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VEUhAVki0DA</a>"},{"pid":"ebb58cc8e9b57952ef94ae4fdd068ab5fc2815f0","tid":1488980,"uid":289818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T18:08:42.000Z","msg":"p牌係咪推唔到post?"},{"pid":"50034c2cf490362e6af2af2ccde1cf72f16c73d9","tid":1488980,"uid":290804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T18:09:20.000Z","msg":"&lt;821&gt;咁撚大件事冇人講 全撚同我入